      p I’m using #[a(href="https://expressjs.com/") express.js] for my web server, and signaling it to render my .pug files as HTML. That await right there is the crux of the whole operation. It outputs a list of inline HTML that I then shove into the home page as links to the individualized pages I render from the markdown.
      pre.hljs
